                        React components and add them directly to
                        the main navigation, or to documents</p>
                </div>
                <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-12">
                    <div class="lg:px-8 lg:col-span-6 relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
                        <CodeBlock
                                language="typescript"
                                code={`export function ProductDetailPreview({ modifiedValues }: {
    modifiedValues?: EntityValues<Product>;
